Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 1^reset;

You've begun to learn how to make useful crop-growing aids out of chemicals and can now craft basic fertilizer at your ^orange;Alchemy Table^reset;

Ammonium Sulfate can be extracted from many sources. Try grinding up some Core Fragments or Poop in your Hand Mill.

You'll need a ^orange;Growing Tray^reset; to do anything with your fertilizer - if you're just growing plants out of the ground with a hoe and watering can, it won't be of any use to you.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;1级^reset;

你已经学会了液体创造的基础知识，现在可以在你的实验室里人工创造几种不同的液体类型。

你还学会了培育细胞材料，这是培育新型植物时的有用资源。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 1^reset;

You've learned the basics of liquid creation and can now artifically create a few different liquid types at your lab.

You've also learned to create Cell Material, a useful resource when engineering novel plants.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;1级^reset;

你已经自学了一些基本的医学知识，可以制作简单的治疗物品。

^yellow;你知道吗？^reset;Frackin' Universe的治疗物品在使用后会有一段适度长的冷却时间，在此期间不能使用其他治疗物品。不要期望一遍打架一边用绷带包扎伤口！

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 1^reset;

You've taught yourself some basic medical knowledge and can make simple healing items.

^yellow;Did you know?^reset; Healing items in Frackin' Universe impose a moderately long cooldown upon use during which no other healing items can be used. Don't expect to spam bandages to victory!

Texts.Chs:
^orange;2级^reset;

显微镜非常有用。显微镜允许你扫描蜜蜂的基因性能，以及生产研究过的文物和造物的数据。

这台显微镜可用^orange;自动组装器^reset;装配。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 2^reset;

Microscopes are extremely useful, allowing you to scan Bees for their genetic capabilities as well as generate research from investigated artifacts and equipment.

This microscope is available in an ^orange;Auto-Assembler^reset;.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;2级^reset;

你现在知道如何制造更多种类的液体，包括一些非常热或非常冷的液体。

有了工程化的拼接细胞，你就可以进行更进一步的基因工程。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 2^reset;

You now know how to make a few more types of liquid, including some really hot or really cold ones.

With the engineered Spliced Cell, you have access to even greater genetic engineering.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;3级^reset;

现在你可以制造出更好的显微镜，提高生产效率。

这台显微镜可以在^orange;物质汇编机^reset;处组装。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 3^reset;

You're able to create much better microscopes now, enhancing your production rates.

This microscope is available in a ^orange;Matter Assembler^reset;.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;4级^reset;

通过激进的实验，你已经学会了创造一种神奇的物质，它不仅有相位物质的奇特属性，同时具有难以置信的耐久和高度可塑性。除了用于武器和装甲，它还具有很好的导电性，可以制造出令人惊叹的新型电子设备。

你对相位材料的了解也使你能够在实验室里创造出对一些不同的深奥反应有用的原料块。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 4^reset;

Through intense experimentation, you've learned to create an amazing substance that exploits the strange properties of phase matter to be simultaneously incredibly durable and highly moldable. Besides its use in weapons and armor, it's also quite conductive and will allow amazing new electronic devices to be made.

Your knowledge of phasic materials has also allowed you to create 'blocks' of raw matter in your lab that are useful for a couple different esoteric reactions.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;4级^reset;

你的显微镜越来越好了，可以放大到极致，清晰度极高。

这台显微镜可以在^orange;物质汇编机^reset;处组装。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 4^reset;

Your microscopes are getting quite good now, allowing extreme zoom and fantastic clarity.

This microscope is available in a ^orange;Matter Assembler^reset;.

Texts.Chs:
^orange;5级^reset;

你的显微镜是一件美丽的神器，它可以让你看到前所未知的微观世界。

这台显微镜可以在^orange;能源设备制造器^reset;处组装。

Texts.Eng:
^orange;Tier 5^reset;

Your microscopes are a thing of beauty, allowing you to see into microcosms previously unknown.

This microscope is available in a ^orange;Power Station^reset;.
